import { Button, Navbar, Container, Nav } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark">
        <Container>
          <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Mi Proyecto</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Toggle />
          <Navbar.Collapse className="justify-content-end">
            <Navbar.Text>
              Usuario
            </Navbar.Text>
          </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
      </Navbar>
    
    </>
  )
}

export default Header
